Plot_X_Axis $xmin $xmax $x_tick_spacing $ymin
Plot_Y_Axis $ymin $ymax $y_tick_spacing $xmin
Label_X_Ticks $xmin $xmax $x_tick_spacing
Label_Y_Ticks $ymin $ymax $y_tick_spacing
.

